org.apache.lucene.queryParser.core.processors

Class RemoveDeletedQueryNodesProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.queryParser.core.processors.QueryNodeProcessorImpl
      • org.apache.lucene.queryParser.core.processors.RemoveDeletedQueryNodesProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryNodeProcessor

    public class RemoveDeletedQueryNodesProcessor
extends QueryNodeProcessorImpl
    A QueryNodeProcessorPipeline class removes every instance of DeletedQueryNode from a query node tree. If the resulting root node is a DeletedQueryNode, MatchNoDocsQueryNode is returned.
